Metadata: Northwest Fish Hatchery Newsletter (Volume 8, Number 1, February 1992)
Oregon State University Extension/Sea Grant Program
This was the last newsletter issue received by the NSGL.
The following topics are in this issue: Fish Sampling Methods, D. V. Buchanan; Low Head Oxygen System, J. Sheahan; New Electrofishing Technology Applied to Adult Sorting, M. Evenson.
